yes, wolf &amp; crane is the newest bar in little tokyo. it is super chill, hip and best of all, unpretentious. they have a good number of craft beers and tasty mixed cocktails. there's no food &nbsp;but i was told by the bartender that you can bring in outside food. <span class="highlighted">happy hour</span> is weeknights, 5-7there's jazz night, game night and also a dj spinning on different nights of the week!look out for the logo of a wolf &amp; a crane when trying to find this place. it's also right next to subway!cheers!
