nes can take you to civic center station, where the edison is just a 5 minute walk away.overall, it was another great <span class="highlighted">happy hour</span>. &nbsp;great vibe at <span class="highlighted">happy hour</span> and there was no line to get into the place. &nbsp;i love their martinis and tesla fries!
