e so if you're not a fan of black licorice and want a safe choice, this isn't it. total spent: &nbsp;$32. &nbsp;<span class="highlighted">happy hour</span>....awesome.we also ordered the elvis which was a total binge considering its like a french toast with peanut butter (creamy as hell and didn't really stick like a jif commercial), bananas, and caramel dipping sauce. &nbsp;amazing stuff, but this was not on special and cost more than one of the specialty drinks.spending about $6.40 a drink in one of the coolest looking bars you'll ever see was well worth it.definitely recommend this to anyone.
